        📍 ${geo.city}, ${geo.country}<br>
        🏢 ${geo.isp} · ${geo.type}<br>
        📝 ${count} review${count>1?'s':''} · 🚨 ${fakeCount} fake<br>
        ⚠ Risk Score: <span style="color:${riskColor};font-weight:700">${risk}%</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ip-bar-wrap"><div class="ip-bar" style="width:${risk}%;background:${riskColor}"></div></div>
